      • getFilteredArtifacts

        public Set<org.apache.maven.artifact.Artifact> getFilteredArtifacts(Iterable<org.apache.maven.artifact.Artifact> allArtifacts,
                                                           String... types)
        Filters provided artifacts and selects only defined types based on types argument or all types if types argument is empty.
        Parameters:
        allArtifacts - artifacts to be filtered
        types - artifact types to be selected
        Returns:
        a List of all project dependencies. Never null. This excludes artifacts of the EXCLUDED_DEPENDENCY_SCOPES scopes. And this should maintain dependency order to comply with library project resource precedence.

        Filters provided artifacts and selects only defined types based on types argument or all types if types argument is empty.
        Parameters:

        types - artifact types to be selected
        Returns:
